gololang.ir

Class ReferenceLookup

  • java.lang.Object
    • gololang.ir.GoloElement<T>
      • gololang.ir.GoloStatement<T>
        • gololang.ir.ExpressionStatement<ReferenceLookup>
          • gololang.ir.ReferenceLookup

  • public final class ReferenceLookup
extends ExpressionStatement<ReferenceLookup>
    A reference lookup in the golo code.

    This expression represents every reference use, that is when a variable is considered as an expression.
